WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:02.543
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.543 --> 00:03.384
WAIT FOR ME!

00:03.384 --> 00:04.465
I'M SORRY, POPPET.

00:04.465 --> 00:07.178
NO! VICTORIA!

00:07.178 --> 00:08.799
I WAS LOCKED UP
AGAINST MY WILL.

00:08.799 --> 00:11.392
I CANNOT ENTERTAIN
A FUTURE WITH YOU

00:11.392 --> 00:13.134
UNTIL SHE'S BEEN STOPPED.

00:13.134 --> 00:15.226
TELL ME WHO IT IS.

00:15.226 --> 00:16.807
HER NAME IS EMILY THORNE.

00:16.807 --> 00:18.189
TAKE IT EASY, MAN!

00:18.189 --> 00:19.640
THAT'S NOT MINE.
 YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

00:19.640 --> 00:21.272
Margaux:
GIDEON IS GOING TO PRISON.

00:23.484 --> 00:25.906
I'M BEGGING YOU, CHARLOTTE.
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.
 OH, GOD.

00:27.568 --> 00:28.529
[ GRUNTS ]

00:29.650 --> 00:31.992
I'M YOUR SISTER, CHARLOTTE.
I'M AMANDA.

00:38.038 --> 00:40.000
GOODBYE, SIS.

00:40.000 --> 00:41.082
IS ANYONE ELSE IN THERE?

00:41.082 --> 00:43.294
NO. IT'S EMPTY.

00:57.228 --> 00:58.479
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

00:58.479 --> 00:59.560
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

00:59.560 --> 01:01.442
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!
THERE'S NO ONE IN THERE!

01:01.442 --> 01:03.484
IT'S MY BAR!
I CAN'T JUST LET IT BURN!

01:03.484 --> 01:06.357
THE FIRE DEPARTMENT'S
ON THEIR WAY!

01:13.114 --> 01:14.995
[ COUGHING ]

01:24.084 --> 01:25.836
EMILY!

01:33.634 --> 01:35.426
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

01:35.426 --> 01:37.178
COME ON. COME ON.
COME ON.

01:39.770 --> 01:41.222
Man: I NEED MORE PRESSURE
OVER HERE.

01:41.222 --> 01:43.644
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

01:51.532 --> 01:54.114
HELP!
SOMEONE HELP!

01:54.114 --> 01:55.826
OVER HERE! [ COUGHING ]
 HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY.

01:55.826 --> 01:58.118
YOU OKAY? WHAT HAPPENED?

01:58.118 --> 01:59.200
SHE WAS INSIDE!

01:59.200 --> 02:01.001
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

02:01.001 --> 02:03.204
I GOT YOU.
 [ COUGHING ]

02:03.204 --> 02:05.206
CAN YOU OPEN YOUR EYES
FOR ME?

02:07.127 --> 02:08.959
HEY.
 [ COUGHING ]

02:08.959 --> 02:11.091
CHECK YOUR PULSE.

02:11.091 --> 02:13.093
YOU'RE OKAY.
YOU'RE OKAY.

02:16.387 --> 02:18.639
GET THESE PEOPLE BACK!
MOVE BACK!

02:18.639 --> 02:20.020
[ COUGHING ]

02:23.854 --> 02:26.767
Man: BRING HER BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL.

02:38.118 --> 02:39.200
[ LAUGHS ]

02:39.200 --> 02:41.282
LOST FOR WORDS, ARE YOU?

02:41.282 --> 02:42.373
[ LAUGHS ]

02:42.373 --> 02:45.746
I SEEM TO REMEMBER A SUMMER
10 YEARS AGO

02:45.746 --> 02:48.749
WHEN THIS KIND OF THING HAPPENED
ON OCCASION.

02:48.749 --> 02:51.922
AND I COULDN'T GET YOU
TO SHUT UP.

02:51.922 --> 02:53.594
MAYBE I'M A DIFFERENT
PERSON NOW.

02:53.594 --> 02:54.635
I'LL SAY.

02:54.635 --> 02:58.259
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

03:00.261 --> 03:03.013
YOU KNOW,
YOU'RE WELCOME TO STAY.

03:03.013 --> 03:04.225
MORE THAN WELCOME.

03:04.225 --> 03:05.936
I HAVE A BIG MORNING.

03:05.936 --> 03:09.270
I CALLED AN EMERGENCY
BOARD MEETING AT LeMARCHAL.

03:09.270 --> 03:10.361
RIGHT.

03:10.361 --> 03:13.314
TO MANAGE YOUR BROTHER'S
NOT-SO-QUIET EXIT.

03:13.314 --> 03:16.527
AND FIND A NEW C.O.O.
BEFORE SHAREHOLDERS PANIC.

03:16.527 --> 03:20.120
I MEAN, WHO HAS TO HIRE
THREE C.O.O.s IN SIX MONTHS?

03:20.120 --> 03:22.202
I'M STARTING TO LOOK
LIKE AN IDIOT.

03:22.202 --> 03:23.704
MM. OUCH.

03:23.704 --> 03:25.205
NO, NO, NO, NO,
THAT CAME OUT WRONG.

03:25.205 --> 03:26.707
NO, I WASN'T REFERRING
TO YOU.

03:26.707 --> 03:28.419
I DIDN'T MEAN TO MAKE YOU
UNCOMFORTABLE.

03:28.419 --> 03:29.790
DON'T WORRY.
YOU DIDN'T.

03:29.790 --> 03:31.252
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

03:31.252 --> 03:33.043
YOU ACTUALLY INSPIRED ME.

03:33.043 --> 03:34.295
TOMORROW MORNING,

03:34.295 --> 03:36.006
THE GUCCI COMES OUT
OF THE COLD STORAGE,

03:36.006 --> 03:39.009
AND MY ASSAULT
ON WALL STREET BEGINS.

03:39.009 --> 03:41.141
DAMN RIGHT IT DOES.

03:54.815 --> 03:56.487
SERIOUSLY?

03:56.487 --> 03:59.320
SOMEBODY BETTER HAVE DIED.

04:03.033 --> 04:04.034
WAIT!

04:04.034 --> 04:06.126
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
IT WAS VACANT.

04:06.126 --> 04:08.629
WHAT IF THERE'S
AN ALARM?

04:11.962 --> 04:13.674
THERE'S NO SENSORS
IN THE DOORJAMBS,

04:13.674 --> 04:15.876
NO MOTION DETECTORS,
NO STICKER IN THE WINDOW.

04:15.876 --> 04:16.797
I THINK WE'RE OKAY.

04:28.148 --> 04:31.151
THIS WILL DO FOR NOW.

04:31.151 --> 04:32.523
SHOTGUNS.

04:32.523 --> 04:33.734
GOOD TO HAVE.

04:33.734 --> 04:35.275
WE WON'T NEED THEM.

04:35.275 --> 04:38.529
WE'LL STAY QUIET,
KEEP THE BLINDS DRAWN.

04:38.529 --> 04:40.110
NO ONE WILL KNOW
WE'RE HERE.

04:40.110 --> 04:42.162
YEAH, LIKE PRISONERS.

04:42.162 --> 04:43.744
NOT PRISONERS.

04:43.744 --> 04:46.166
WE'RE JUST BEING CAREFUL.

04:46.166 --> 04:47.668
IT'S ONLY TEMPORARY.

04:47.668 --> 04:50.080
TOMORROW, I'LL GO SEE
MY BANKER,

04:50.080 --> 04:52.623
AND WE'LL START LOOKING
FOR A PLACE OF OUR OWN.

04:52.623 --> 04:55.125
I'LL LEAVE IN THE MORNING
AND BE BACK BY NOON.

04:55.125 --> 04:56.176
I'M GOING WITH YOU.

04:56.176 --> 04:57.718
YOU CAN'T.

04:57.718 --> 04:59.590
WHAT ABOUT
THIS EMILY THORNE?

04:59.590 --> 05:01.472
WHAT IF SHE
FINDS YOU FIRST?

05:01.472 --> 05:03.594
SHE BETTER HOPE
SHE DOESN'T.

05:03.594 --> 05:06.186
YOU NEED TO STAY INSIDE
FOR JUST A WHILE LONGER.

05:06.186 --> 05:07.808
I CANNOT LOSE YOU AGAIN,
DAVID.

05:07.808 --> 05:09.690
ONCE THE WORLD FINDS OUT
ABOUT YOU,

05:09.690 --> 05:12.232
THERE'LL BE QUESTIONS --
QUESTIONS ABOUT CONRAD.

05:12.232 --> 05:14.645
AND ONCE YOU'RE DONE
ANSWERING THEM,

05:14.645 --> 05:17.067
WE WON'T HAVE
A MOMENT TO OURSELVES.

05:17.067 --> 05:19.740
AND I'M SELFISH.
I CAN'T HELP IT.

05:19.740 --> 05:23.033
I DON'T WANT TO SHARE YOU
UNTIL I HAVE TO.

05:41.091 --> 05:42.342
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

05:42.342 --> 05:43.424
[ COUGHING ]

05:43.424 --> 05:45.225
DUDE, I JUST HEARD
ON THE RADIO.

05:45.225 --> 05:47.097
I GOT HERE
AS FAST AS I COULD.

05:47.097 --> 05:48.769
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
 [ SIGHS ] YEAH.

05:48.769 --> 05:51.351
YEAH, I GOT A FEW
BUMPS AND BRUISES,

05:51.351 --> 05:53.734
AND MY THROAT HURTS
FROM THE SMOKE, BUT...

05:53.734 --> 05:54.815
I'LL BE OKAY.

05:54.815 --> 05:57.027
YOU ACTUALLY RAN
INTO A BURNING BUILDING?

05:57.027 --> 05:59.480
YOU DO REALIZE THEY DON'T
PAY US EXTRA FOR THAT, RIGHT?

05:59.480 --> 06:02.032
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH, WELL...

06:02.032 --> 06:03.654
I'M GLAD I DID.

06:03.654 --> 06:06.196
SO, YOU WERE WALKING PAST
YOUR FRIEND'S BAR,

06:06.196 --> 06:08.078
AND YOU SMELLED SMOKE?

06:08.078 --> 06:09.159
[ COUGHING ]

06:09.159 --> 06:10.370
I WENT INSIDE TO SEE

06:10.370 --> 06:13.414
IF IT WAS SOMETHING SMALL
THAT I COULD PUT OUT,

06:13.414 --> 06:17.127
BUT ONCE I GOT IN,
IT WAS OUT OF CONTROL.

06:17.127 --> 06:20.631
SOMETHING MUST'VE FALLEN
ON MY HEAD BECAUSE...

06:20.631 --> 06:23.964
NEXT THING I KNEW,
JACK WAS CARRYING ME OUT.

06:23.964 --> 06:26.807
WE HAVE TO GET HER TO A HOSPITAL
FOR A C.A.T. SCAN.

06:26.807 --> 06:27.928
ONE MORE QUESTION.

06:27.928 --> 06:29.890
WAS THERE
ANYONE ELSE INSIDE?

06:31.892 --> 06:33.353
MISS THORNE...

06:33.353 --> 06:35.896
DID YOU SEE
ANYONE ELSE?

06:37.978 --> 06:40.110
NO.

06:40.110 --> 06:43.323
NO, THERE WAS
NO ONE ELSE INSIDE.

06:43.323 --> 06:44.364
JUST ME.

06:59.039 --> 07:01.131
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

07:01.131 --> 07:03.383
EMS?

07:03.383 --> 07:05.966
[ SCOFFS ]
WELL, DON'T GET UP.

07:05.966 --> 07:08.679
THESE WERE SUPPOSED TO SPRUCE UP
YOUR HOSPITAL ROOM,

07:08.679 --> 07:10.010
BUT I JUST CAME FROM THERE,

07:10.010 --> 07:14.434
AND, WEIRDLY,
IT'S EMPTY AND UNSPRUCED.

07:14.434 --> 07:16.316
I CHECKED MYSELF OUT.

07:16.316 --> 07:19.189
IT'S A HOSPITAL,
NOT A HOTEL.

07:19.189 --> 07:20.440
[ SIGHS ]

07:20.440 --> 07:22.943
I RAN INTO YOUR DOCTOR,

07:22.943 --> 07:24.945
AND HE SAID THAT YOUR LUNGS
SUSTAINED SOME DAMAGE

07:24.945 --> 07:26.947
BUT THAT YOU ARE
VERY LUCKY.

07:26.947 --> 07:28.028
ANOTHER FEW MINUTES,

07:28.028 --> 07:30.531
YOU COULD'VE DIED
OF SMOKE INHALATION.

07:30.531 --> 07:32.783
SEE, THIS IS WHAT I HATE
ABOUT DOCTORS.

07:32.783 --> 07:33.744
THEY EXAGGERATE.

07:33.744 --> 07:34.995
YOU KNOW WHAT?
FINE.

07:34.995 --> 07:37.077
PRETEND
YOU'RE INDESTRUCTIBLE,

07:37.077 --> 07:38.999
BUT SUPERHEROES
DON'T GET BALLOONS.

07:38.999 --> 07:41.502
AND THIS ISN'T
JUST A SICK CALL.

07:41.502 --> 07:43.173
I COME
BEARING INFORMATION.

07:43.173 --> 07:44.925
ACCORDING TO TWITTER,

07:44.925 --> 07:47.087
YOUR RUNAWAY LUNATIC,
VICTORIA GRAYSON,

07:47.087 --> 07:49.510
JUST EMERGED
FROM HER AIRBNB IN HELL

07:49.510 --> 07:51.221
OR WHATEVER HOLE
SHE CRAWLED OUT OF.

07:51.221 --> 07:53.183
WHEN?

07:53.183 --> 07:54.765
LESS THAN AN HOUR AGO.

07:54.765 --> 07:59.810
IN MIDTOWN MANHATTAN.

07:59.810 --> 08:02.312
AND YOU'RE NOT MOVING.

08:02.312 --> 08:04.605
YOU'RE STILL NOT MOVING.
AND WHY ARE YOU NOT MOVING?

08:04.605 --> 08:07.407
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
I HAVE TO DO TODAY.

08:07.407 --> 08:09.069
I JUST TELL YOU
THAT YOUR ARCHENEMY,

08:09.069 --> 08:11.702
WHO DECLARED ALL-OUT WAR ON YOU
LESS THAN 48 HOURS AGO,

08:11.702 --> 08:13.453
HAS SURFACED, BUT...

08:13.453 --> 08:16.416
WELL, YOU'VE GOT
MORE...PRESSING MATTERS.

08:16.416 --> 08:19.039
THAT'S WHAT I SAID.

08:21.171 --> 08:22.332
OKAY.

08:24.384 --> 08:26.046
I WOULD NOT WANT TO BE

08:26.046 --> 08:29.129
NUMBER ONE
ON YOUR TO-DO LIST TODAY.

08:32.011 --> 08:33.303
DANIEL.

08:37.017 --> 08:38.018
DANIEL.

08:38.018 --> 08:39.229
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:39.229 --> 08:41.270
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

08:41.270 --> 08:42.602
LOOKING FOR YOU.

08:42.602 --> 08:45.195
I KNOW THIS IS
YOUR FAVORITE HOTEL.
 REALLY?

08:45.195 --> 08:47.197
YOU RUN AWAY FOR THE WORST
SIX MONTHS I CAN REMEMBER,

08:47.197 --> 08:49.239
AND NOW YOU WANT TO CHAT
ABOUT MY TASTE IN LODGING?

08:49.239 --> 08:51.071
I DID NOT RUN AWAY.
 NO, WAIT, NO, WAIT,
I APOLOGIZE.

08:51.071 --> 08:53.654
I DID GET YOUR POSTCARD
FROM BHUTAN,

08:53.654 --> 08:56.206
AND I WOULD'VE WRITTEN YOU BACK
IF I WASN'T BUSY

08:56.206 --> 08:58.789
DUCKING EVERY SINGLE REPORTER
IN THE COUNTRY.

08:58.789 --> 09:03.083
WHAT, YOU FIGURED
IT'S FINALLY SAFE TO COME HOME?

09:03.083 --> 09:04.625
STOP IT NOW AND LISTEN.

09:04.625 --> 09:06.506
I HAVE NEVER ABANDONED YOU.

09:06.506 --> 09:08.338
WHAT DO YOU WANT, MOTHER?

09:08.338 --> 09:11.011
IS THIS THE WAY
IT'S GOING TO BE?

09:11.011 --> 09:12.673
OKAY.

09:12.673 --> 09:15.225
I JUST CAME BACK
FROM THREE DIFFERENT BANKS.

09:15.225 --> 09:17.978
EVERY ACCOUNT
THAT CAN BE TRACED BACK TO ME,

09:17.978 --> 09:19.179
ONSHORE, OFFSHORE,

09:19.179 --> 09:21.982
HAS EITHER BEEN FROZEN
OR SEIZED BY THE GOVERNMENT.

09:21.982 --> 09:23.103
YEAH,
THAT SOUNDS ABOUT RIGHT.

09:23.103 --> 09:24.564
SO, TO GET US
BACK ON OUR FEET,

09:24.564 --> 09:28.318
I NEED ACCESS TO ANY ASSETS
OR FUNDS YOU MAY HAVE HIDDEN.

09:28.318 --> 09:29.990
WHAT ASSETS OR FUNDS?

09:29.990 --> 09:31.451
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

09:31.451 --> 09:33.654
YOU ARE THE PATRIARCH
OF THIS FAMILY NOW.

09:33.654 --> 09:35.866
THAT'S WHAT
THE GRAYSON MEN DO.

09:35.866 --> 09:38.538
HOW DO YOU NOT PUT MONEY ASIDE
TO PREPARE FOR A RAINY DAY?

09:38.538 --> 09:40.080
BECAUSE PREPARING
FOR A RAINY DAY

09:40.080 --> 09:41.121
IS THE EXACT BEHAVIOR

09:41.121 --> 09:43.373
THAT BROUGHT ON A DAMN MONSOON
SIX MONTHS AGO,

09:43.373 --> 09:44.795
RIGHT WHEN YOU DISAPPEARED.

09:44.795 --> 09:46.877
AND ONE DAY,
I WILL TELL YOU EVERYTHING,

09:46.877 --> 09:48.588
BUT UNTIL THEN,
ALL YOU NEED TO KNOW

09:48.588 --> 09:50.470
IS THAT I'M GOING TO MAKE
THIS FAMILY WHOLE AGAIN.

09:50.470 --> 09:52.552
OKAY, WELL,
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

09:52.552 --> 09:55.215
OH, AND SINCE YOU CARE
SO MUCH,

09:55.215 --> 09:56.176
YOU MIGHT WANT TO KNOW

09:56.176 --> 09:57.718
THAT CHARLOTTE'S HANGING OUT
WITH DRUG DEALERS,

09:57.718 --> 09:59.219
SHOVING GOD KNOWS WHAT
UP HER NOSE,

09:59.219 --> 10:02.272
AND SHE ALMOST TOOK A LEAP
OFF THE MAISON HOTEL.

10:02.272 --> 10:03.603
SO THAT'S THE UPDATE.

10:03.603 --> 10:05.435
LET'S DO THIS AGAIN
IN ANOTHER SIX MONTHS.

10:30.130 --> 10:33.213
THEY SAID IT STARTED
BEHIND THE WALL.

10:33.213 --> 10:35.886
IT'S ALL
THAT OLD WIRING.

10:35.886 --> 10:37.808
KEPT MEANING
TO UPGRADE IT,

10:37.808 --> 10:40.470
BUT THERE WAS ALWAYS
SOMETHING ELSE TO DO.

10:40.470 --> 10:42.102
NEVER --
NEVER GOT AROUND TO IT.

10:42.102 --> 10:45.395
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

10:45.395 --> 10:47.027
STUFF HAPPENS.

10:47.027 --> 10:50.320
MY DAD KEPT THIS PLACE GOING
FOR THREE DECADES.

10:50.320 --> 10:53.073
I CAN'T BELIEVE
IT WENT AWAY OVERNIGHT.

10:55.275 --> 10:59.039
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE TO BEGIN.

11:01.201 --> 11:03.043
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,

11:03.043 --> 11:05.876
WHENEVER I START CODING
A NEW PIECE OF SOFTWARE,

11:05.876 --> 11:07.998
IT INVARIABLY
SEEMS OVERWHELMING.

11:07.998 --> 11:10.130
SO WHAT I DO IS THIS.

11:10.130 --> 11:13.173
I ASK MYSELF,
WHAT SINGLE PART

11:13.173 --> 11:15.255
OF THIS PROJECT
IS MOST IMPORTANT TO ME?

11:15.255 --> 11:18.008
SOMETIMES
THAT GETS ME STARTED.

11:18.008 --> 11:20.600
YOUR MILEAGE MAY VARY.

11:20.600 --> 11:25.395
YEAH, MAYBE I'LL SEARCH
FOR WHATEVER PHOTOS OR MEMENTOS

11:25.395 --> 11:27.687
I CAN SALVAGE,
STUFF THAT'S...

11:27.687 --> 11:29.439
THAT'S IRREPLACEABLE.

11:29.439 --> 11:30.771
GOOD PLAN.

11:30.771 --> 11:34.524
I'LL GO GET A BIN
FOR THE REST OF IT.

11:34.524 --> 11:35.736
[ SIGHS ]

11:45.205 --> 11:48.088
EXCUSE ME. JACK?

11:48.088 --> 11:50.170
TOM MULLEN.
I JUST WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

11:50.170 --> 11:52.502
I WAS HERE --
 LAST NIGHT.
AT THE FIRE.

11:52.502 --> 11:53.964
YOU WERE THE GUY WHO TOLD ME
THERE WAS NO ONE IN HERE.

11:53.964 --> 11:55.005
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?!
 I'M SO SORRY.

11:55.005 --> 11:57.337
I DIDN'T KNOW.
IT'S WHAT THAT GIRL TOLD ME.

11:57.337 --> 11:58.338
WHAT GIRL?

11:58.338 --> 11:59.639
THE ONE WHO RAN
OUT OF THE BAR.

11:59.639 --> 12:00.841
BEFORE YOU GOT HERE.

12:00.841 --> 12:03.263
19, MAYBE 20.

12:03.263 --> 12:04.845
I THINK SHE WORKED HERE
LAST SUMMER.

12:21.411 --> 12:22.492
VICTORIA?

12:22.492 --> 12:25.245
VICTORIA!

12:25.245 --> 12:26.246
[ LAUGHS ]

12:26.246 --> 12:27.868
LOUISE?!

12:29.419 --> 12:30.540
HOW DID YOU --

12:30.540 --> 12:31.872
I GOT OUT OF CLAREMONT!

12:31.872 --> 12:34.004
OH, THANK GOD!

12:34.004 --> 12:36.046
YOU REALIZE I DIDN'T INTEND
TO LEAVE YOU THERE.

12:36.046 --> 12:38.178
YOU UNDERSTAND THAT,
DON'T YOU?

12:38.178 --> 12:39.429
WELL, IT ALL WORKED OUT.

12:39.429 --> 12:41.721
AFTER YOU ESCAPED,
DR. MILLER LEFT.

12:41.721 --> 12:43.473
YOU KNOW,
I THINK THEY FIRED HIM.

12:43.473 --> 12:47.017
AND HIS REPLACEMENT
REVIEWED MY FILE

12:47.017 --> 12:49.059
AND SAID I WAS
"WRONGFULLY COMMITTED."

12:49.059 --> 12:51.151
AMAZING, RIGHT?

12:51.151 --> 12:52.482
YES, IT IS!

12:52.482 --> 12:54.064
WELL, LET'S SPEND
THE DAY TOGETHER,

12:54.064 --> 12:56.106
CELEBRATE OUR FREEDOM.

12:56.106 --> 12:57.858
LOUISE, I'M SORRY.
I CAN'T.

12:57.858 --> 13:00.400
WELL, WHY NOT?

13:00.400 --> 13:02.202
LOOK, THE TRUTH IS...

13:02.202 --> 13:03.994
I HAVE NOWHERE TO GO.

13:03.994 --> 13:07.247
I WAS HOPING WE COULD TALK,
LIKE WE USED TO BACK IN --

13:07.247 --> 13:09.830
LOUISE, I AM IN SURVIVAL MODE
RIGHT NOW.

13:09.830 --> 13:12.042
MY CHILDREN NEED ME.
THEY'RE IN GREAT DISTRESS.

13:12.042 --> 13:14.214
I HAVE NO RESOURCES.

13:14.214 --> 13:16.086
OKAY? NOTHING.

13:16.086 --> 13:19.009
I'M SORRY.
I HAVE TO GO.

13:19.009 --> 13:20.510
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT.

13:20.510 --> 13:21.801
UH, I CAN HELP YOU.

13:21.801 --> 13:23.133
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

13:23.133 --> 13:24.634
GO HOME, LOUISE.

13:24.634 --> 13:25.846
SEE YOUR MOTHER.

13:25.846 --> 13:27.097
MY MOTHER?

13:27.097 --> 13:30.060
HAVE YOU FORGOTTEN
WHAT I TOLD YOU ABOUT HER?

13:30.060 --> 13:32.812
DARLING, THERE'S REALLY NOTHING
I CAN DO TO HELP YOU NOW.

13:32.812 --> 13:36.196
WHEN THINGS CHANGE,
I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

13:56.216 --> 13:58.168
OH, MY GOD.

14:08.018 --> 14:11.231
JACK, I'M SO SORRY.

14:11.231 --> 14:14.104
YOU GOT MY MESSAGE?

14:14.104 --> 14:15.025
YEAH.

14:15.025 --> 14:19.149
YOU HAD
A COUPLE QUESTIONS?

14:19.149 --> 14:21.241
YEAH, WELL...

14:21.241 --> 14:24.074
I WAS HOPING
YOU COULD HELP ME...

14:24.074 --> 14:27.117
UNDERSTAND
WHAT HAPPENED LAST NIGHT.

14:27.117 --> 14:29.199
I TOLD YOU.

14:29.199 --> 14:30.750
I GAVE MY STATEMENT.

14:30.750 --> 14:32.122
I KNOW YOU DID,

14:32.122 --> 14:34.995
BUT THERE'S STILL
A COUPLE THINGS I DON'T GET.

14:34.995 --> 14:37.167
LIKE WHAT WAS CHARLOTTE
DOING HERE?

14:37.167 --> 14:40.460
EMILY, I TALKED TO A WITNESS
WHO SAID HE THINKS HE SAW HER

14:40.460 --> 14:42.052
RUNNING OUT OF HERE
LAST NIGHT.

14:42.052 --> 14:43.883
DON'T -- DON'T TREAT ME
LIKE I'M AN IDIOT!

14:43.883 --> 14:44.804
WHAT HAPPENED?!
 IT DEPENDS.

14:44.804 --> 14:46.176
AM I TALKING
TO JACK PORTER MY FRIEND

14:46.176 --> 14:48.308
OR JACK PORTER OF THE SUFFOLK
COUNTY POLICE DEPARTMENT?

14:48.308 --> 14:50.100
YOU'RE TALKING TO THE GUY
WHO -- WHO WATCHED

14:50.100 --> 14:52.182
A HUGE PART OF HIS LIFE
GO UP IN FLAMES LAST NIGHT

14:52.182 --> 14:54.184
AND DESERVES
TO KNOW WHY!

14:58.478 --> 15:00.941
[ SIGHS ]

15:00.941 --> 15:04.024
YESTERDAY, AFTER WE TALKED
AND CHARLOTTE RAN OFF,

15:04.024 --> 15:05.155
SHE CALLED.

15:05.155 --> 15:06.866
SHE WAS CALMER.
SHE SAID...

15:06.866 --> 15:08.989
SHE WANTED TO MEET
AT THE STOWAWAY

15:08.989 --> 15:10.530
AND ASK A FEW QUESTIONS.

15:10.530 --> 15:12.993
IT NEVER OCCURRED TO ME
NOT TO BELIEVE HER.

15:12.993 --> 15:13.994
SO...

15:13.994 --> 15:17.087
ARE YOU SAYING
THAT SHE AMBUSHED YOU?

15:17.087 --> 15:18.878
I DIDN'T SEE IT COMING.

15:18.878 --> 15:21.091
SHE KNOCKED ME OUT AND...

15:21.091 --> 15:23.173
SET THE BAR ON FIRE.

15:23.173 --> 15:25.465
AND SHE LEFT YOU FOR DEAD.
WHY ARE YOU COVERING FOR HER?

15:25.465 --> 15:27.347
'CAUSE AFTER EVERYTHING
THAT I HAVE PUT HER THROUGH --

15:27.347 --> 15:29.599
WHAT?
YOU DESERVED IT?

15:29.599 --> 15:31.141
SHE TRIED TO KILL YOU,
EMILY!

15:31.141 --> 15:32.973
SO, NOW WHAT?
YOU -- YOU GUYS ARE EVEN?

15:32.973 --> 15:34.814
SHE JUST WALKS AWAY?
 I'LL HANDLE IT.

15:34.814 --> 15:36.106
[ SCOFFS ]
THAT CAN'T BE YOUR ANSWER!

15:36.106 --> 15:37.227
[ STAMMERS ]

15:37.227 --> 15:38.979
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO
WITH "I'LL HANDLE IT"?

15:38.979 --> 15:40.230
WHAT DOES THAT
EVEN MEAN?!

15:40.230 --> 15:42.522
IT MEANS I'M STICKING
TO MY STATEMENT, JACK.

15:42.522 --> 15:45.155
NO ONE ELSE
WAS IN THE BAR.

15:45.155 --> 15:47.277
I'M GONNA DEAL WITH THIS
THE WAY I HAVE TO.

15:47.277 --> 15:48.698
FEEL FREE TO DO THE SAME.

15:53.743 --> 15:55.955
[ PILLS RATTLING ]

15:59.339 --> 16:01.081
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

16:10.510 --> 16:12.182
[ SIGHS ]

16:17.647 --> 16:20.020
OH, MY ANGEL!

16:20.020 --> 16:21.941
[ GASPS ] OH!

16:21.941 --> 16:23.063
I KNOW.

16:23.063 --> 16:26.236
YOU'VE BEEN ALL ALONE,

16:26.236 --> 16:27.907
AND I HAVEN'T BEEN THERE
FOR YOU.

16:32.572 --> 16:34.114
IT'S SO MUCH MORE
THAN THAT.

16:34.114 --> 16:35.035
IT'S OKAY.

16:35.035 --> 16:36.786
I'M HERE NOW.

16:36.786 --> 16:40.080
CHARLOTTE,
TELL ME EVERYTHING.

16:40.080 --> 16:41.381
[ SIGHS ]

16:49.889 --> 16:51.841
CHARLOTTE?

16:51.841 --> 16:55.975
EMILY THORNE
IS AMANDA CLARKE.

16:55.975 --> 16:58.728
AND SHE'S BEEN LYING ABOUT IT
THIS WHOLE TIME.

17:02.102 --> 17:04.144
HOW DID YOU LEARN
OF THIS?

17:04.144 --> 17:06.146
SHE TOLD ME.

17:06.146 --> 17:10.319
EITHER OUT OF GUILT
OR SHAME OR...

17:10.319 --> 17:13.203
JUST TO TORTURE ME.

17:13.203 --> 17:16.205
DID YOU KNOW?

17:16.205 --> 17:20.119
I'VE SUSPECTED
FOR SOME TIME.

17:20.119 --> 17:21.711
I WANTED TO GET
CONFIRMATION

17:21.711 --> 17:23.423
AND FIND THE RIGHT TIME
TO TELL YOU,

17:23.423 --> 17:26.126
BUT WHEN I CONFRONTED HER,
SHE DENIED IT.

17:26.126 --> 17:27.217
BUT DON'T YOU WORRY.

17:27.217 --> 17:29.008
THAT PATHOLOGICAL CREATURE

17:29.008 --> 17:31.131
IS GOING TO GET
WHAT SHE DESERVES.

17:31.131 --> 17:34.304
AND WHAT ABOUT ME?

17:34.304 --> 17:36.096
WILL I?

17:36.096 --> 17:37.387
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

17:39.099 --> 17:40.770
WHAT DID YOU DO?

17:40.770 --> 17:43.523
I TRIED TO KILL HER.

17:43.523 --> 17:45.525
LAST NIGHT,

17:45.525 --> 17:50.190
I-I WENT OUT OF MY MIND,
AND I STARTED A FIRE.

17:50.190 --> 17:51.861
BUT SHE SURVIVED.

17:51.861 --> 17:53.613
AND SHE KNOWS
IT WAS ME.

17:53.613 --> 17:55.865
AND I HAVE NEVER BEEN
MORE AFRAID.

17:55.865 --> 17:58.248
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT SHE'S CAPABLE OF.
 OH, I DO.

17:58.248 --> 18:00.580
SHE'S THE ONE
WHO KIDNAPPED ME.

18:00.580 --> 18:01.961
AND SHE'LL COME
AFTER ME AGAIN!

18:01.961 --> 18:03.373
I WON'T LET HER.

18:03.373 --> 18:06.126
YOU'RE SAFE NOW.

18:06.126 --> 18:08.338
YOU'RE GOING TO COME LIVE
WITH US.

18:08.338 --> 18:09.969
AND WE'LL PROTECT YOU.

18:09.969 --> 18:12.212
WE?

18:12.212 --> 18:13.133
MM-HMM.

18:13.133 --> 18:14.093
WHO ELSE?

18:16.596 --> 18:18.638
YOUR FATHER, CHARLOTTE.

18:18.638 --> 18:22.312
YOUR REAL FATHER.

18:22.312 --> 18:24.314
DAVID CLARKE IS ALIVE.

18:26.726 --> 18:27.687
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

18:27.687 --> 18:28.728
WHAT HAPPENED?

18:28.728 --> 18:30.280
I WAS JUST COMING DOWN
TO MEET YOU

18:30.280 --> 18:31.571
WHEN THE DOORMAN CALLED.

18:31.571 --> 18:33.443
THEY GIVE AWAY YOUR TABLE
AT BALTHAZAR?

18:33.443 --> 18:35.495
NAH, MAN,
THAT PLACE IS SO LOUD.

18:35.495 --> 18:37.157
I HATE IT.

18:37.157 --> 18:38.368
I HAD A BETTER IDEA.

18:38.368 --> 18:40.500
I GRABBED SOME SANDWICHES
FROM ZABAR'S.

18:40.500 --> 18:41.701
I GOT CORNED BEEF.

18:41.701 --> 18:44.043
I FIGURED WE COULD JUST,
YOU KNOW, MAYBE CHILL.

18:44.043 --> 18:45.795
EAT IT HERE?

18:45.795 --> 18:48.748
I MEAN, IT IS --
IS A KICK-ASS PAD.

18:48.748 --> 18:52.051
WHERE NO ONE ON THE STREET
WILL SPOT YOU WITH ME.

18:52.051 --> 18:54.053
COME ON,
IT'S NOT EXACTLY LIKE THAT.

18:54.053 --> 18:55.215
IT'S A LITTLE
LIKE THAT.

18:57.177 --> 18:59.058
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN STRAIGHT
WITH YOU,

18:59.058 --> 19:02.021
EVEN BACK WHEN I TOLD YOU I WAS
GONNA COPY YOUR ECON FINAL.

19:02.021 --> 19:04.224
LOOK, I TRIED TO GET YOU
INTO OUR FIRM,

19:04.224 --> 19:05.645
BUT THAT WAS A NONSTARTER.

19:05.645 --> 19:08.067
PRITCHARD DOESN'T EVEN WANT ME
TALKING TO YOU.

19:08.067 --> 19:09.359
WHAT?
YOU SERIOUS?

19:09.359 --> 19:10.650
YEAH.

19:10.650 --> 19:12.942
AND I MADE SOME MORE CALLS
TO PUSH YOU FURTHER,

19:12.942 --> 19:14.444
BUT IT'S A BROKEN RECORD.

19:14.444 --> 19:16.736
BLACKSTONE PEOPLE,
MORGAN STANLEY,

19:16.736 --> 19:19.279
THEY HEAR YOUR LAST NAME,
AND THEY SHUT DOWN.

19:19.279 --> 19:20.910
WHAT,
SO NO ONE'S GONNA HIRE ME?

19:20.910 --> 19:22.452
NOBODY'S GONNA MEET
 WITH YOU.

19:22.452 --> 19:25.124
IT'S NOT GONNA BE
LIKE THAT FOREVER.

19:25.124 --> 19:27.457
FINANCE HAS A SHORT MEMORY.

19:27.457 --> 19:29.839
AND WHAT DO I DO
IN THE MEANTIME, JAMIE?

19:29.839 --> 19:32.171
GET AWAY FOR A WHILE --
SIX MONTHS, A YEAR.

19:32.171 --> 19:34.294
TAKE SOME TIME
AND SMELL THE ROSES.

19:34.294 --> 19:37.176
GIVE PEOPLE A CHANCE TO MOVE ON
TO THE NEXT SCANDAL.

19:41.351 --> 19:43.182
OKAY.

19:43.182 --> 19:45.605
Charlotte: [ SIGHS ]

19:45.605 --> 19:49.188
CAN YOU TELL
I'VE BEEN CRYING?

19:49.188 --> 19:51.070
I WANT THE FIRST TIME
I MEET HIM TO BE --

19:51.070 --> 19:53.813
OH, CHARLOTTE.
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

19:53.813 --> 19:55.525
NOW, REMEMBER
WHAT I TOLD YOU.

19:55.525 --> 19:58.278
WE CAN'T OVERLOAD DAVID.
HE'S FRAGILE.

19:58.278 --> 20:00.910
THERE ARE SOME THINGS
THAT WE CAN'T ASK HIM

20:00.910 --> 20:02.992
AND OTHERS
THAT WE CAN'T TELL HIM.

20:02.992 --> 20:03.993
NOT YET.

20:06.165 --> 20:08.498
LIKE THE FACT
THAT AMANDA'S STILL ALIVE?

20:08.498 --> 20:09.919
TRUST ME,

20:09.919 --> 20:12.832
YOUR FATHER WILL FIND OUT
ABOUT HIS OTHER DAUGHTER,

20:12.832 --> 20:15.134
AND WHEN HE DOES,
IT'LL BE THE REAL STORY

20:15.134 --> 20:17.507
OF HOW SHE VICIOUSLY
DEDICATED HERSELF

20:17.507 --> 20:19.839
TO OUR DESTRUCTION
AND OUR SUFFERING.

20:24.103 --> 20:25.975
HE'S GOING TO LOVE YOU.

20:28.728 --> 20:31.060
OH...

20:31.060 --> 20:32.151
OH, MY GOD.

20:33.613 --> 20:34.274
CHARLOTTE?

20:36.025 --> 20:37.236
[ LAUGHS ]

20:37.236 --> 20:38.488
DAVID,
MEET YOUR DAUGHTER.

20:38.488 --> 20:39.859
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:49.459 --> 20:52.462
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:52.462 --> 20:54.173
Nolan: I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DID IT,

20:54.173 --> 20:57.587
BUT YOU MANAGED
TO KNOCK THE WHOLE
SECURITY SYSTEM OFFLINE

20:57.587 --> 20:59.589
WHEN YOU MESSED
WITH THE TERMINAL.

20:59.589 --> 21:01.180
UH, IT'S MY HOUSE,
NOLAN,

21:01.180 --> 21:03.723
SO BY DEFINITION,
I DIDN'T MESS WITH ANYTHING.

21:03.723 --> 21:04.974
I JUST USED IT.

21:04.974 --> 21:07.056
OKAY, THIS IS NOT
A TOASTER OVEN.

21:07.056 --> 21:10.229
THIS IS A HIGHLY CALIBRATED CPU
WITH AN INT--

21:10.229 --> 21:14.023
OKAY, FINE,
BE TECHNOLOGICALLY IGNORANT.

21:14.023 --> 21:18.027
WHAT'S SO IMPORTANT
ABOUT 1760 SOUTH PINE ROAD?

21:18.027 --> 21:19.449
WHAT'S THERE?

21:19.449 --> 21:22.161
SOMEONE
I NEED TO TALK TO.

21:22.161 --> 21:24.203
I USED YOUR VERY IMPRESSIVE
COMPUTER --

21:24.203 --> 21:25.164
TO A PING A CELLPHONE.

21:25.164 --> 21:26.666
CHARLOTTE'S, RIGHT?

21:26.666 --> 21:28.328
WHAT?
I CONNECTED THE DOTS.

21:28.328 --> 21:30.169
SO, WHAT IS THE PLAN
ANYWAY --

21:30.169 --> 21:32.712
GO FIND HER HIDEAWAY
AND RETURN THE FAVOR?

21:32.712 --> 21:35.124
I DON'T KNOW -- MAYBE SLAP
BABY SIS AROUND A LITTLE,

21:35.124 --> 21:38.087
GET PAYBACK
FOR TRYING TO KILL YOU.
 I AM NOT GONNA GO HURT HER.

21:38.087 --> 21:39.469
THEN WHAT?

21:39.469 --> 21:41.130
OH, NO.

21:41.130 --> 21:42.472
NO, NO.

21:42.472 --> 21:44.724
NO, YOU DON'T THINK THAT
YOU CAN TALK TO HER, DO YOU?

21:44.724 --> 21:46.806
REHABILITATE HER,
HAVE AN OPRAH MOMENT.

21:46.806 --> 21:47.887
THAT PLAN IS WORSE.

21:47.887 --> 21:49.559
IT WON'T WORK.
 YOU DON'T KNOW THAT.

21:49.559 --> 21:51.190
I KNOW THAT YOU TOLD HER
EVERYTHING

21:51.190 --> 21:52.522
AND SHE REJECTED YOU

21:52.522 --> 21:54.394
AND THEN TRIED TO TOAST YOU
LIKE A MARSHMALLOW.

21:54.394 --> 21:56.315
WHAT'S TO BE GAINED?
 I DON'T KNOW, OKAY?

21:56.315 --> 21:58.778
ALL I KNOW IS I MESSED
WITH CHARLOTTE'S LIFE,

21:58.778 --> 22:00.820
AND SHE DIDN'T DESERVE IT.

22:00.820 --> 22:02.241
NOLAN,
SHE IS IN SO MUCH PAIN.

22:02.241 --> 22:03.823
AND SHE IS NOT
THE ONLY ONE.

22:03.823 --> 22:05.284
I ALMOST LOST YOU
LAST NIGHT.

22:05.284 --> 22:06.616
I'M STILL HERE.

22:06.616 --> 22:09.158
AND I'M GOING TO TRY TO GET
THROUGH TO CHARLOTTE AGAIN.

22:09.158 --> 22:11.831
YOU CAN TRY TO STOP ME, BUT WE
BOTH KNOW HOW THAT WILL END UP.

22:11.831 --> 22:13.953
ALL RIGHT,
DO YOU HAVE A PLAN?

22:13.953 --> 22:14.754
NO.

22:14.754 --> 22:15.755
OKAY, PERFECT --

22:15.755 --> 22:17.627
NO PLAN,
NO LIST OF BAD GUYS,

22:17.627 --> 22:19.459
NO PHOTOGRAPH WITH
THEIR FACES ON IT, NOTHING.

22:19.459 --> 22:20.880
SO, WHAT,

22:20.880 --> 22:22.842
YOU'RE JUST GONNA WALK BLINDLY
INTO THE LINE OF FIRE?

22:22.842 --> 22:25.805
SOMETIMES
THAT'S THE ONLY WAY IN.

22:32.311 --> 22:33.683
David:
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:33.683 --> 22:36.355
I REMEMBER YOUR EYES.

22:36.355 --> 22:38.147
YOU COULDN'T.

22:38.147 --> 22:40.109
WHEN DID YOU SEE ME?

22:40.109 --> 22:42.442
I BROUGHT YOU TO THE COURTHOUSE
WHEN YOU WERE A BABY

22:42.442 --> 22:44.073
SO HE COULD SEE
YOUR FACE.

22:44.073 --> 22:47.827
I LOOKED CLOSE IN CASE
I NEVER GOT ANOTHER CHANCE.

22:47.827 --> 22:49.989
HOW DID THIS HAPPEN?

22:49.989 --> 22:52.662
HOW IS IT THAT YOU'RE SITTING
RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME?

22:52.662 --> 22:54.203
[ SIGHS ]

22:54.203 --> 22:56.255
I KNOW
THAT THIS ISN'T FAIR,

22:56.255 --> 22:59.208
BUT I'D RATHER HEAR
MORE ABOUT YOU.

22:59.208 --> 23:01.260
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE TO START.

23:01.260 --> 23:03.503
TELL HIM
ABOUT THE PAST FEW YEARS.

23:03.503 --> 23:05.555
THEY WEREN'T EASY
FOR ANY OF US,

23:05.555 --> 23:07.637
AND I CERTAINLY
WASN'T AT MY BEST,

23:07.637 --> 23:09.929
BUT CHARLOTTE
WAS ALWAYS MY TOUCHSTONE.

23:09.929 --> 23:11.851
SHE WAS EVERYTHING
THAT WAS GOOD.

23:11.851 --> 23:13.893
AND WHENEVER
I FELT LIKE GIVING UP,

23:13.893 --> 23:17.276
I JUST HAD TO LOOK
AT HER FACE.

23:17.276 --> 23:19.148
REALLY?
 MM-HMM.

23:19.148 --> 23:22.111
FROM THE MOMENT SHE KNEW
THAT YOU WERE HER FATHER,

23:22.111 --> 23:24.113
SHE WAS DETERMINED
TO PROVE YOUR INNOCENCE.

23:24.113 --> 23:26.195
YOU WERE?
 MOM, STOP.

23:26.195 --> 23:29.078
IT WAS CHARLOTTE
WHO ELICITED CONRAD'S CONFESSION

23:29.078 --> 23:31.080
FOR ALL THE WORLD
TO HEAR.

23:31.080 --> 23:32.742
DAVID,
SHE EXONERATED YOU.

23:34.454 --> 23:36.456
I-I THINK I'M FEELING
A LITTLE, UH --

23:36.456 --> 23:38.958
NO, I-I-I GET IT.

23:38.958 --> 23:40.710
I THINK THIS WHOLE THING
HAS TO BE...

23:40.710 --> 23:43.042
REALLY OVERWHELMING.

23:43.042 --> 23:46.175
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK, IT'S GETTING COLD.

23:46.175 --> 23:47.967
I'LL SEE IF I CAN FIND
SOME FIREWOOD.

23:47.967 --> 23:49.509
CHARLOTTE...

23:49.509 --> 23:52.391
I AM SO HAPPY
TO MEET YOU.

23:58.147 --> 24:00.359
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

24:00.359 --> 24:03.442
EVERYTHING YOU TOLD HIM
WASN'T TRUE.

24:03.442 --> 24:05.114
I TOLD HIM NO LIES.

24:05.114 --> 24:07.026
BUT ISN'T THE REAL ME
GOOD ENOUGH?

24:07.026 --> 24:08.197
OH, CHARLOTTE.

24:08.197 --> 24:11.120
I WISH YOU COULD SEE
WHAT I SEE.

24:11.120 --> 24:13.743
THAT THE REAL YOU
IS BETTER THAN EVEN YOU KNOW.

24:13.743 --> 24:16.035
OH.

24:16.035 --> 24:17.497
YOU'RE RUNNING ON FUMES,
DARLING.

24:17.497 --> 24:19.959
LIE DOWN.
GET SOME REST. HERE.

24:26.085 --> 24:28.087
WELL, MAYBE YOUR FRIEND
WAS EXAGGERATING.

24:28.087 --> 24:30.550
HE COULDN'T HAVE TALKED
TO EVERY FIRM IN THE CITY.

24:30.550 --> 24:32.642
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT,
SO I MADE SOME CALLS

24:32.642 --> 24:33.553
AFTER HE LEFT.

24:33.553 --> 24:35.354
THEY ALL SAID
THE SAME THING.

24:35.354 --> 24:38.648
I MEAN, WITH A STORY LIKE MINE,
I DON'T THINK I'D HIRE ME.

24:38.648 --> 24:39.859
THERE IS A WAY
THAT I CAN HELP.

24:39.859 --> 24:42.231
NO, I-I CAN'T GO BACK
TO LeMARCHAL.

24:42.231 --> 24:45.154
NO, I'M NOT SUGGESTING THAT,
BUT AS C.E.O.,

24:45.154 --> 24:46.445
I CAN EXPLAIN
YOUR DEPARTURE

24:46.445 --> 24:48.157
AND GET A HALF DOZEN
UPPER-LEVEL EXECS

24:48.157 --> 24:49.779
TO SIT DOWN WITH YOU.
 MARGAUX,
IT'S NOT AN OPTION.

24:49.779 --> 24:51.450
THERE ARE PEOPLE
WHO OWE ME FAVORS.

24:51.450 --> 24:52.992
WHICH IS WHY
YOU CAN'T DO IT.

24:52.992 --> 24:54.914
SPENDING YOUR CAPITAL
TO VOUCH FOR ME

24:54.914 --> 24:57.376
WILL DAMAGE YOUR COMPANY,
YOUR CREDIBILITY AS C.E.O.

24:57.376 --> 24:58.998
I DON'T CARE.
 WELL, I DO.

24:58.998 --> 24:59.999
WHY?

24:59.999 --> 25:02.121
WHY?

25:02.121 --> 25:05.084
BECAUSE YOU'VE WORKED HARD
FOR IT.

25:05.084 --> 25:06.546
AND...

25:06.546 --> 25:08.798
AND...?

25:08.798 --> 25:11.931
IT MIGHT BE NICE
TO HAVE ONE THING IN MY LIFE

25:11.931 --> 25:14.053
THAT ISN'T
A COMPLETE DISASTER.

25:14.053 --> 25:18.017
SO I'M YOUR INCOMPLETE
DISASTER?

25:18.017 --> 25:20.439
WELL, SO FAR.

25:20.439 --> 25:21.731
OKAY.

25:35.414 --> 25:36.576
[ MUG THUDS ]

25:42.872 --> 25:45.004
THAT'S CLOSE ENOUGH.

25:46.586 --> 25:48.167
I'M NOT HERE FOR YOU.

25:48.167 --> 25:50.840
I'M HERE
TO TALK TO CHARLOTTE.

25:50.840 --> 25:52.471
YOU WON'T BE TALKING
TO ANYONE

25:52.471 --> 25:55.014
FOR THE REST OF WHAT'S ABOUT
TO BECOME A VERY SHORT LIFE

25:55.014 --> 25:57.516
UNLESS YOU GET
THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

25:57.516 --> 25:59.018
CHARLOTTE'S INSIDE.

25:59.018 --> 26:01.060
I'M NOT LEAVING
UNTIL I TALK TO HER.

26:01.060 --> 26:01.941
CHARLOTTE?

26:01.941 --> 26:05.234
CHARLOTTE, IT'S EMILY.

26:05.234 --> 26:08.067
I JUST WANT TO TALK TO YOU,
NOTHING MORE.

26:08.067 --> 26:10.820
ONLY THE TWO OF US
KNOW EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED

26:10.820 --> 26:12.531
AT THE STOWAWAY
LAST NIGHT.

26:12.531 --> 26:14.904
AND THAT'S HOW
IT'S GOING TO STAY.

26:14.904 --> 26:17.456
YOU HAVE MY WORD.

26:18.788 --> 26:20.329
[ SIGHS ]

26:20.329 --> 26:21.961
I KNOW
YOU'RE IN A BAD PLACE.

26:21.961 --> 26:25.665
AND IT'S A PLACE
THAT I HELPED PUT YOU.

26:25.665 --> 26:29.669
BUT I WANT YOU TO KNOW THAT,
WHETHER YOU BELIEVE ME OR NOT,

26:29.669 --> 26:32.171
I AM TRULY SORRY.

26:32.171 --> 26:34.513
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]
 ENOUGH OF YOUR LIES.

26:34.513 --> 26:36.265
NOW GO, EMILY,
OR I SWEAR TO GOD, I WILL --

26:36.265 --> 26:38.097
WHAT ARE YOU
WAITING FOR?

26:39.138 --> 26:41.270
YOU KEEP LOOKING TO THE WOODS
LIKE YOU'RE WAITING

26:41.270 --> 26:42.932
FOR THE CAVALRY
TO COME SAVE YOU.

26:42.932 --> 26:44.724
I'M NOT THE ONE
WHO NEEDS SAVING.

26:44.724 --> 26:45.725
SO DO IT.

26:45.725 --> 26:47.276
SHOOT.

26:47.276 --> 26:51.030
END THIS WHOLE THING
RIGHT NOW.

26:53.492 --> 26:55.154
NO.

26:55.154 --> 26:57.576
THAT WOULD BE TOO EASY.

26:57.576 --> 27:00.910
I OWE YOU SO MUCH MORE
THAN A QUICK DEATH.

27:03.332 --> 27:05.244
BUCKLE UP, SWEETHEART.

27:29.438 --> 27:30.980
OFFICER HUNTER.

27:30.980 --> 27:32.772
WHOA!

27:32.772 --> 27:33.612
CAN I HELP YOU?

27:33.612 --> 27:35.234
YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T
SNEAK UP

27:35.234 --> 27:36.696
ON A GUY IN UNIFORM
LIKE THAT.

27:36.696 --> 27:39.038
I'M -- I'M LIABLE TO --
 ACCIDENTALLY SHOOT ME?

27:39.038 --> 27:41.160
I WAS GONNA SAY
"GASP IN A REALLY UNMANLY WAY,"

27:41.160 --> 27:44.623
BUT, YEAH, I GUESS THAT'S --
THAT'S POSSIBLE, TOO.

27:44.623 --> 27:46.205
I HEARD ABOUT THAT FIRE.

27:46.205 --> 27:48.207
I'M GLAD
YOU'RE DOING ALL RIGHT.

27:48.207 --> 27:50.289
YEAH, THANKS.

27:50.289 --> 27:53.052
SO, WHAT ARE YOU DOING
OUT HERE?

27:53.052 --> 27:54.423
I WAS --
I WAS INVESTIGATING

27:54.423 --> 27:56.175
REPORTS OF KIDS DRINKING
UP IN THESE WOODS.

27:56.175 --> 28:00.890
AND I SAW WHAT LOOKED LIKE
AN ABANDONED VEHICLE.

28:00.890 --> 28:02.892
MAYBE A MOTORIST
IN DISTRESS.

28:02.892 --> 28:06.105
COOL CAR, BY THE WAY.
IT'S ELECTRIC, YEAH?

28:06.105 --> 28:08.307
SO, WHERE DOES IT,
YOU KNOW, PLUG IN?

28:08.307 --> 28:10.309
IT'S TOP SECRET.

28:10.309 --> 28:11.400
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

28:11.400 --> 28:13.112
NO, BUT AS YOU CAN SEE,

28:13.112 --> 28:15.524
THE CAR'S NOT ABANDONED,
I'M NOT IN DISTRESS,

28:15.524 --> 28:17.576
AND, NO,
I HAVE NOT BEEN DRINKING.

28:17.576 --> 28:19.989
I WASN'T GONNA ASK.

28:21.240 --> 28:24.123
MAYBE I WAS GONNA ASK
WHAT YOU WERE DOING OUT HERE...

28:24.123 --> 28:25.624
IN THE MIDDLE OF NOWHERE.

28:25.624 --> 28:26.746
[ SIGHS ]

28:26.746 --> 28:29.749
WELL, I LIKE TO GET OUT
AND CLEAR MY HEAD.

28:29.749 --> 28:31.630
SOME PEOPLE
LIKE TO GO TO THE BEACH.

28:31.630 --> 28:34.834
I GO FOR A WALK
IN THE WOODS.

28:34.834 --> 28:36.045
IT'S STILL LEGAL,
RIGHT?

28:36.045 --> 28:38.007
YES.
YES, I THINK SO.

28:38.007 --> 28:39.298
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:39.298 --> 28:41.720
LISTEN, FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,
I'M THE SAME WAY.

28:41.720 --> 28:43.722
I'M A "WALK IN THE WOODS"
KIND OF GUY.

28:43.722 --> 28:46.725
SO, SHOULD YOU EVER WANT
ANY COMPANY...

28:46.725 --> 28:49.769
OKAY.

28:55.444 --> 28:58.567
YOU'RE NOT EVER GONNA WANT
COMPANY, ARE YOU?

28:58.567 --> 29:02.281
PROBABLY NOT.

29:06.415 --> 29:08.127
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

29:14.253 --> 29:15.334
SIMON.

29:15.334 --> 29:16.876
IS THERE A PROBLEM?

29:16.876 --> 29:18.547
[ SIGHS ]
YOUR BILL.

29:18.547 --> 29:20.719
IT HASN'T BEEN PAID
IN TWO MONTHS.

29:20.719 --> 29:22.301
YOU LEFT US NO CHOICE.

29:22.301 --> 29:24.553
DID YOU TRY
MY CREDIT CARD?

29:24.553 --> 29:25.724
DECLINED.

29:25.724 --> 29:28.187
I TOOK THE LIBERTY
OF PACKING UP YOUR SUITE

29:28.187 --> 29:29.148
AND CHECKING YOU OUT.

29:29.148 --> 29:31.060
YOUR BAGS
WILL BE DOWNSTAIRS.

29:31.060 --> 29:33.482
YOU'VE BEEN A VALUED GUEST,
MR. GRAYSON.

29:33.482 --> 29:35.444
WE WISH YOU
THE BEST OF LUCK.

29:39.028 --> 29:40.109
OH.

29:40.109 --> 29:43.402
WILL YOU BE NEEDING
A TAXI VOUCHER?

29:43.402 --> 29:45.034
NO. THANKS.

29:47.166 --> 29:49.578
AM I STILL WELCOME
IN THE HOTEL BAR?

29:49.578 --> 29:50.619
ABSOLUTELY.

29:50.619 --> 29:52.171
AS LONG
AS YOU PAY CASH.

29:52.171 --> 29:53.082
MM.

29:56.215 --> 29:58.467
YOU STARED DOWN
THE BARREL OF A SHOTGUN

29:58.467 --> 30:01.130
HELD BY VICTORIA'S
BITCHY TRIGGER FINGER,

30:01.130 --> 30:03.092
AND YOU DARED HER
TO SHOOT YOU?

30:03.092 --> 30:05.134
REMIND ME NEVER TO PLAY POKER
WITH YOU.

30:05.134 --> 30:07.636
I WASN'T BLUFFING.

30:07.636 --> 30:09.768
WELL, MAYBE
CONSIDER YOURSELF LUCKY

30:09.768 --> 30:11.810
SHE DIDN'T HAVE THE GUTS
TO DO IT.

30:11.810 --> 30:13.232
IT WASN'T LUCK OR GUTS.

30:13.232 --> 30:14.353
VICTORIA DIDN'T SHOOT ME
BECAUSE --

30:14.353 --> 30:16.435
BECAUSE SHE DIDN'T WANT TO DO IT
IN FRONT OF CHARLOTTE.

30:16.435 --> 30:17.526
NO, THAT WOULDN'T STOP HER,

30:17.526 --> 30:19.028
ALTHOUGH
CHARLOTTE IS THE REASON

30:19.028 --> 30:20.359
I'M NOT HEADING OVER THERE
RIGHT NOW

30:20.359 --> 30:22.151
TO WRAP THAT GUN
AROUND VICTORIA'S NECK.

30:22.151 --> 30:25.154
NO, VICTORIA...

30:25.154 --> 30:27.156
HAS SOMETHING ELSE PLANNED.

30:27.156 --> 30:29.288
FOR THREE YEARS,

30:29.288 --> 30:33.082
I'VE WATCHED AND PREDICTED
HER EVERY MOVE.

30:33.082 --> 30:35.794
BUT THIS, I...

30:35.794 --> 30:37.416
I CAN'T SEE IT.

30:37.416 --> 30:40.419
I'M MISSING
PART OF THE PICTURE.

30:40.419 --> 30:41.840
WHAT DID SHE SAY
TO YOU?

30:41.840 --> 30:45.094
SHE OWES YOU SO MUCH MORE
THAN A QUICK DEATH?

30:45.094 --> 30:49.058
IT WAS THE WAY
SHE SAID IT...

30:51.060 --> 30:53.232
...LIKE SHE KNOWS
SOMETHING I DON'T.

30:55.314 --> 30:58.187
WELL, ON A COMPLETELY
UNRELATED NOTE,

30:58.187 --> 31:00.940
I'M GONNA CRASH HERE
FOR A COUPLE OF NIGHTS,

31:00.940 --> 31:02.111
BUNK IN THE POOL HOUSE,

31:02.111 --> 31:04.483
REBOOT
THE SECURITY SYSTEM,

31:04.483 --> 31:06.155
KEEP AN EYE ON YOU.

31:06.155 --> 31:07.036
[ SCOFFS ]

31:07.036 --> 31:09.038
A COMPLETELY
UNRELATED NOTE?

31:09.038 --> 31:11.080
WELL, I WON'T TAKE NO
FOR AN ANSWER.

31:11.080 --> 31:12.992
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:19.458 --> 31:21.460
I AM DIGGING THE NEW LOOK.

31:21.460 --> 31:25.674
OH, YEAH, I'M GOING FOR
A POST-APOCALYPTIC BAR THING.

31:25.674 --> 31:27.216
IT'S COOL.
VERY "MAD MAX."

31:27.216 --> 31:29.058
I THINK THE TOURISTS
WILL EAT IT UP.

31:29.058 --> 31:30.179
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:30.179 --> 31:31.810
EVERYBODY AT THE STATION
SENDS THEIR BEST.

31:31.810 --> 31:33.012
MM.
 AND THE, UH, THE WORD

31:33.012 --> 31:35.474
FROM OUR DALMATIAN-LOVING
FRIENDS ACROSS THE STREET

31:35.474 --> 31:37.726
IS THAT FIRE INVESTIGATION'S
RULING IT AN ACCIDENT.

31:39.818 --> 31:40.899
THEY'RE QUICK.

31:40.899 --> 31:42.191
WELL, LOOK,
YOU'RE ON THE FORCE,

31:42.191 --> 31:43.692
SO AS A PROFESSIONAL
COURTESY,

31:43.692 --> 31:46.155
THEY'LL KEEP IT OPEN
IF YOU WANT.

31:46.155 --> 31:47.736
AND THEY'LL EVEN PUT IN
MORE MAN-HOURS,

31:47.736 --> 31:49.658
SO IF YOU'RE NOT READY
TO CLOSE THE BOOK ON IT,

31:49.658 --> 31:51.620
JUST SAY THE WORD.

31:55.294 --> 31:57.666
NO, NAH.
THEY KNOW WHAT THEY'RE DOING.

31:57.666 --> 31:59.838
I MEAN,
IT -- IT HAD TO BE THE WIRING.

31:59.838 --> 32:01.750
I KEPT MEANING
TO UPGRADE IT.

32:01.750 --> 32:03.502
LET 'EM CLOSE IT.

32:03.502 --> 32:05.804
WELL, SILVER LINING --

32:05.804 --> 32:07.926
WITH THE INSURANCE MONEY,
YOU UPGRADE THE WHOLE PLACE.

32:07.926 --> 32:10.099
BUILD YOURSELF
A BRAND-NEW BAR.

32:10.099 --> 32:12.181
WHY DOES THAT SOUND
LIKE A LIFE SENTENCE

32:12.181 --> 32:13.602
MORE THAN A SILVER LINING?

32:13.602 --> 32:14.813
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

32:18.317 --> 32:20.189
SHE WAS IN THE HOUSE?!

32:20.189 --> 32:21.270
I WOULDN'T LET HER IN.

32:21.270 --> 32:24.193
WELL, YOU COULD'VE SHOUTED TO ME
OR FIRED A WARNING SHOT.

32:24.193 --> 32:25.194
I WANTED TO,

32:25.194 --> 32:27.066
BUT I WAS AFRAID
WHO ELSE MIGHT HEAR.

32:27.066 --> 32:28.827
WHAT DID SHE WANT?

32:28.827 --> 32:30.489
CHARLOTTE.
 WHAT?

32:30.489 --> 32:33.162
I THOUGHT IT -- THAT
IT WAS YOU THAT SHE WAS AFTER.
 I TOLD YOU,

32:33.162 --> 32:35.164
EMILY WANTS TO DESTROY
OUR WHOLE FAMILY.

32:35.164 --> 32:38.207
SHE FOUND US SO QUICKLY.
HOW DID SHE DO THAT?
 THAT'S WHAT SHE DOES.

32:38.207 --> 32:40.789
TOMORROW, WE'RE GOING TO LOOK
FOR ANOTHER PLACE TO STAY.

32:40.789 --> 32:42.671
BUT WE STILL NEED MONEY.

32:42.671 --> 32:44.043
I'M GOING TO TOWN.

32:44.043 --> 32:45.794
THERE'S ONE MORE SOURCE
I HAVEN'T TAPPED.

32:45.794 --> 32:47.136
THEN I'M COMING WITH YOU.
 NO!

32:47.136 --> 32:48.587
STAY HERE, PLEASE!

32:48.587 --> 32:50.049
CHARLOTTE'S SLEEPING.

32:50.049 --> 32:51.720
PROTECT OUR DAUGHTER.

32:51.720 --> 32:53.472
PLEASE.

33:27.046 --> 33:28.547
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

33:34.473 --> 33:35.594
JACK.

33:35.594 --> 33:36.555
HEY.

33:36.555 --> 33:38.687
I WAS JUST HEADING TO BED.

33:38.687 --> 33:40.439
OH, WELL,
THEN I'LL BE QUICK.

33:40.439 --> 33:41.850
LOOK, IF THIS IS ABOUT --

33:41.850 --> 33:43.021
THAT'S NOT WHY I'M HERE.

33:45.023 --> 33:48.567
I WAS, UH...

33:48.567 --> 33:50.649
I WAS CLEANING OUT
THE STOWAWAY,

33:50.649 --> 33:52.201
AND I-I FOUND SOMETHING.

33:52.201 --> 33:54.032
I THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT WANT IT.

33:56.575 --> 34:00.329
[ CHUCKLES ]
I REMEMBER THAT DAY.

34:00.329 --> 34:02.331
RIGHT AFTER YOUR DAD
TOOK THIS,

34:02.331 --> 34:05.544
YOU DESTROYED
MY SAND CASTLE.

34:05.544 --> 34:06.585
I TRIPPED.

34:06.585 --> 34:08.507
YOU'RE STILL GOING
WITH THAT STORY?

34:08.507 --> 34:10.799
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

34:10.799 --> 34:13.132
MY DAD KEPT THIS
ON THE WALL

34:13.132 --> 34:15.094
NEXT TO THE --
THE CASH REGISTER

34:15.094 --> 34:17.136
FOR 20-SOMETHING YEARS.

34:17.136 --> 34:19.348
[ CHUCKLES ]
WELL...

34:19.348 --> 34:21.018
I'LL KEEP IT FOR NOW,

34:21.018 --> 34:23.562
BUT ONCE YOU REBUILD,
THEN IT GOES BACK UP.

34:23.562 --> 34:27.946
THE THING IS,
I'VE BEEN THINKING, UM...

34:27.946 --> 34:29.777
WHAT IF I DON'T?

34:29.777 --> 34:31.690
REBUILD.

34:31.690 --> 34:33.572
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

34:33.572 --> 34:35.072
[ SIGHS ]

34:35.072 --> 34:37.196
WHAT, IS IT MONEY?
'CAUSE I CAN HELP.

34:37.196 --> 34:38.996
MNH-MNH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:38.996 --> 34:40.289
JACK, THAT WAS YOUR BAR.

34:40.289 --> 34:41.909
NO, IT WAS MY DAD'S BAR.

34:41.909 --> 34:43.502
HELL, IT WAS HIS DREAM.
IT WAS NEVER MINE.

34:43.502 --> 34:45.083
HE DIDN'T WANT TO
PASS IT ON TO ME.

34:45.083 --> 34:46.415
HE THOUGHT
THE WORLD OF YOU.

34:46.415 --> 34:48.337
THAT'S WHY HE DIDN'T WANT ME
TO HAVE IT.

34:48.337 --> 34:50.047
[ CHUCKLES ]
LOOK BY THE END,

34:50.047 --> 34:52.170
HE KNEW THAT BAR
WAS AN ANCHOR AROUND HIS NECK,

34:52.170 --> 34:54.632
AND HE WANTED ME TO HAVE
A BIGGER LIFE THAN THAT.

34:54.632 --> 34:57.976
THAT'S WHAT I WANTED, TOO.
I JUST...

34:57.976 --> 35:00.639
I DON'T KNOW.
I JUST FORGOT.

35:00.639 --> 35:04.022
SO, WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO?

35:04.022 --> 35:06.315
I'M NOT REALLY SURE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:06.315 --> 35:07.606
UM...

35:07.606 --> 35:09.067
BUT BEING A COP ALL DAY

35:09.067 --> 35:11.109
WHO CLOCKS IN AS A BAR OWNER
AT NIGHT

35:11.109 --> 35:13.692
DOESN'T LEAVE ROOM
FOR MUCH ELSE --

35:13.692 --> 35:15.073
FAMILY, FRIENDS...

35:15.073 --> 35:17.736
PEOPLE I CARE ABOUT.

35:20.579 --> 35:24.122
MAYBE I NEED TO SAY GOODBYE
TO THE STOWAWAY

35:24.122 --> 35:27.916
TO MAKE ROOM IN LIFE
FOR THE THINGS THAT MATTER.

35:30.169 --> 35:34.012
ANYWAY, THAT'S WHAT
I WAS THINKING ABOUT.

35:34.012 --> 35:36.014
YOU, UH...

35:36.014 --> 35:38.927
GET SOME SLEEP.

35:38.927 --> 35:41.350
REST THAT HEAD.

35:41.350 --> 35:43.352
GOOD NIGHT.

35:43.352 --> 35:45.644
JACK?

35:49.438 --> 35:51.149
THANK YOU.

35:53.071 --> 35:54.943
IT'S MY PLEASURE.

35:59.368 --> 36:01.330
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

36:01.330 --> 36:02.741
[ SIGHS ]

36:02.741 --> 36:03.872
Louise: NO.

36:03.872 --> 36:07.045
NO, WHO TOLD YOU
TO SELL THE STOCK?

36:07.045 --> 36:08.877
BECAUSE IT WASN'T ME.

36:08.877 --> 36:12.341
[ SIGHS ]
FINE, CAN IT BE CANCELED?

36:12.341 --> 36:14.463
NO, YOU CALL ME BACK!

36:14.463 --> 36:16.174
WHITE WINE, PLEASE --
NOTHING FROM CALIFORNIA.

36:16.174 --> 36:17.506
Bartender: YOU GOT IT.

36:17.506 --> 36:20.008
WHAT'S WITH HIM?

36:20.008 --> 36:22.471
YOU WERE BEING
A LITTLE LOUD.

36:22.471 --> 36:23.472
OH.

36:23.472 --> 36:25.514
DOING SOME DEEP THINKING,
WERE YOU?

36:25.514 --> 36:28.016
WANT TO PONDER LIFE
IN COMPLETE SILENCE?

36:28.016 --> 36:29.017
FIND A CAVE.

36:29.017 --> 36:31.310
THAT'S GOOD ADVICE.

36:35.113 --> 36:37.025
WAIT, DON'T.
I'M -- I'M SORRY.

36:37.025 --> 36:38.657
T-THAT WAS
INCREDIBLY RUDE.

36:38.657 --> 36:40.028
I'M MAD AT SOMEONE ELSE

36:40.028 --> 36:42.120
AND TOOK IT OUT
ON A COMPLETE STRANGER.

36:42.120 --> 36:43.282
IT HAPPENS.

36:43.282 --> 36:44.873
YEAH?

36:44.873 --> 36:47.125
PEOPLE ALWAYS GETTING MAD AT YOU
FOR NO REASON?

36:47.125 --> 36:49.207
NOT REALLY.

36:49.207 --> 36:51.630
YOU KNOW,
I'M NOT USUALLY THIS CRAZY.

36:51.630 --> 36:54.212
IT'S JUST WHEN MY FAMILY'S
INVOLVED.

36:54.212 --> 36:57.095
AND, OF COURSE,
THEY'RE ALWAYS INVOLVED,

36:57.095 --> 36:58.837
SO, YEAH, CONUNDRUM.

36:58.837 --> 37:01.390
MM.

37:01.390 --> 37:03.302
HERE'S A SECRET
TO LIFE --

37:03.302 --> 37:05.514
DONT BE BORN RICH.

37:07.976 --> 37:09.608
NOW, THAT ACTUALLY
IS GOOD ADVICE.

37:09.608 --> 37:11.560
YEAH, BECAUSE YOU WILL LOSE
ALL CONTROL.

37:11.560 --> 37:13.772
THAT WAS
MY FINANCIAL ADVISER.

37:13.772 --> 37:16.194
HE'S SELLING OFF
MY ENTIRE PORTFOLIO

37:16.194 --> 37:18.196
WITHOUT EVEN
CONSULTING ME.

37:18.196 --> 37:20.319
WELL, WHO PAYS HIM?

37:20.319 --> 37:21.780
WHAT?

37:21.780 --> 37:24.743
YOUR FINANCIAL GUY
ISN'T YOUR FINANCIAL GUY

37:24.743 --> 37:26.325
UNLESS YOU PAY HIS BILL.

37:26.325 --> 37:28.206
THAT'S JUST HOW IT WORKS.

37:28.206 --> 37:29.167
HUH.

37:29.167 --> 37:31.500
OF COURSE IT DOES.

37:31.500 --> 37:33.251
MY MOTHER PAYS HIM.

37:33.251 --> 37:35.334
SO...

37:35.334 --> 37:37.005
DO YOU WORK IN FINANCE?

37:37.005 --> 37:39.378
A LITTLE BIT.

37:39.378 --> 37:41.300
TELL ME...

37:41.300 --> 37:42.801
HOW MUCH DO YOU HATE IT

37:42.801 --> 37:45.143
WHEN PEOPLE ASK YOU
FOR FREE ADVICE?

37:45.143 --> 37:47.846
DEPENDS WHO'S ASKING.

37:52.060 --> 37:54.102
SORRY I DON'T HAVE
MORE TO OFFER.

37:54.102 --> 37:57.065
IF I KNEW YOU'D BE STOPPING BY,
I WOULD'VE ARRANGED DINNER.

37:57.065 --> 37:58.987
OH, PLEASE,
I SHOULD BE APOLOGIZING

37:58.987 --> 38:00.319
FOR DROPPING IN.

38:00.319 --> 38:03.201
BUT I'M SO GLAD
I CAUGHT YOU WORKING LATE.

38:03.201 --> 38:05.614
THE LAST SIX MONTHS
MUST'VE BEEN A NIGHTMARE.

38:05.614 --> 38:09.117
WHO CAN BLAME YOU
FOR DISAPPEARING?

38:09.117 --> 38:10.248
HOW ARE YOU HOLDING UP?

38:10.248 --> 38:13.041
THE TRUTH IS,
I DON'T KNOW.

38:13.041 --> 38:16.044
IT'S LIKE WATCHING
A TRAIN WRECK

38:16.044 --> 38:19.127
AND BEING PART OF IT
AT THE SAME TIME.

38:19.127 --> 38:22.010
CHARLOTTE IS GUTTED
AND DANIEL'S LOST.

38:22.010 --> 38:25.183
I DON'T KNOW HOW MUCH MORE
THIS FAMILY CAN ENDURE.

38:25.183 --> 38:27.976
AND I CAN'T STOP WORRYING
ABOUT ALL OF YOU.

38:27.976 --> 38:31.810
I TOLD YOU
I CONSIDERED YOU FAMILY.

38:31.810 --> 38:35.023
AND YOUR FATHER,
MY BELOVED PASCAL --

38:35.023 --> 38:36.695
GOD REST HIS SOUL...

38:36.695 --> 38:38.146
GOD REST HIS SOUL.

38:38.146 --> 38:41.400
...STILL LIVES IN MY HEART.

38:41.400 --> 38:42.401
SO...

38:45.704 --> 38:49.368
...I WILL ALWAYS THINK OF YOU
AS MY DAUGHTER.

38:49.368 --> 38:51.790
THIS MEANS A LOT.

38:54.292 --> 38:55.584
I, UH...

38:55.584 --> 38:57.005
[ LAUGHS ]

38:57.005 --> 39:00.088
I JUST FEEL
SO POWERLESS.

39:00.088 --> 39:03.301
CONRAD
AND HIS MANIACAL GREED

39:03.301 --> 39:05.964
LAID WASTE
TO OUR FAMILY ASSETS.

39:05.964 --> 39:08.346
THE IDEA OF SEEING MY...

39:08.346 --> 39:12.060
MY CHILDREN PENNILESS
IS JUST...

39:12.060 --> 39:14.433
OH, VICTORIA, I DIDN'T KNOW
THINGS WERE SO DIRE.

39:14.433 --> 39:16.314
DANIEL
DIDN'T EXACTLY LET ON.

39:16.314 --> 39:18.647
HE ALWAYS TRIES TO BE
A GOOD SOLDIER.

39:20.649 --> 39:23.482
LET ME HELP.
GIVE ME A NUMBER.

39:23.482 --> 39:26.034
I'LL WRITE A CHECK.
 NO, MARGAUX,
I CAN'T TAKE ANYTHING FROM YOU.

39:26.034 --> 39:28.537
STOP.
 YOU SAID WE WERE FAMILY.

39:28.537 --> 39:30.659
THIS IS WHAT FAMILY DOES.

39:32.451 --> 39:34.873
WHAT IF WE CALL IT
A LOAN?

39:39.127 --> 39:42.671
ALL RIGHT,
I COULD AGREE TO A LOAN.

40:06.154 --> 40:07.986
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

40:11.079 --> 40:14.412
[ BEEPS ]

40:58.126 --> 40:59.498
EMILY!

40:59.498 --> 41:00.579
EMS.

41:00.579 --> 41:01.710
ARE YOU HURT?

41:08.967 --> 41:10.298
